description: Former Malew commissioner David McWilliams caught the virus after being flown to England for surgery.
title: Covid-19: Ex-Manx commissioner flown to UK for surgery dies
title_page: Covid-19: Ex-Manx commissioner flown to UK for surgery dies - BBC News
maintext: He said it was still safe to travel to the UK for treatment and people should not be "reconsidering their medical treatment".
